GET /api/01/nexus/messages.{json}

Return the latest Nexus messages in the given format.

GET /api/01/nexus/messages/{hash}.{json}

Return the Nexus messages for the given hash in the given format.

GET /api/01/nexus/hashes.{json}

Return the latest message hashes in the given format.

GET /api/01/nexus/hashes/{message_hash}.{json}

Return whether the Nexus has the given message_hash

POST /api/01/nexus/message/update.{json}

(This method will be controlled by OAuth.)

Post a new message to the Nexus timeline.  Required parameter "message" is a JSON-encoded string with the following required members: message_title, message_content, message_hash, message_time, message_type
